Wanna playing? Download and extract it now!
https://github.com/coderhutan/Uler-Snake-Game/archive/master.zip

You must have Ruby Interpreter 1.9.3 installed on your PC.
Download it here http://rubyforge.org/frs/download.php/76798/rubyinstaller-1.9.3-p392.exe
If you're done. Open snake.rb file using the Ruby program on your
C:\Ruby193\bin\ruby.exe


Happy playing! Please share your feedback to me on twitter @irfan3. :)